race.comment: MCKEON (8) has some solid form under her belt and proved too strong last time to win by 1.3 lengths at this track in a handy 27.56 beating WESTERN LIES. Winner at her latest appearance in one of the quickest times on the card. Looks to have an edge on most of these. INTEGRITY SHIRL (4) brought up her 12th career win last start at this track (27.67). Solid record here at the distance winning nine races. Recorded one of the quickest times on the card in scoring last start. Expecting another bold showing. KOORINGA MILLIE (1) goes very well this course and distance starting 10 times for five wins and three minors. Recorded a 2.25 lengths win (27.54) in a NG last time at this track. Can feature in the finish. APACHE TIGER (2) was strongly fancied last time on the back of some superb recent form, including a four-run winning streak, but could only manage second (27.77) at this track. Goes very well from this draw with four wins and two minor placings from seven starts.
